<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9137] solr-script ignores custom STOP_PORT on shutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9137</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When stopping Solr using the script bin/solr a custom STOP_PORT is ignored and always calculated as SOLR_PORT - 1000.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12971505">SOLR-9137</key>
            <summary>solr-script ignores custom STOP_PORT on shutdown</summary>
